      "source": [
        "def create_dataset(dataset,time_step=1):\n",
        "  dataX,dataY=[],[]\n",
        "  for i in range(len(dataset)-time_step-1):\n",
        "    a=dataset[i:(i+time_step),0]\n",
        "    dataX.append(a)\n",
        "    dataY.append(dataset[i+time_step,0])\n",
        "  return np.array(dataX),np.array(dataY)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "vrH4kcM5K9S8"
      },
